    "week 1: Add support for Bash, Zsh, and Fish shell environments",
    "week 1: Implement core fzf-based selector framework",
    "week 1: Integrate `ga`, `gd`, `glo` commands"
  ],
  "acceptance_tests": [
    "Breaking change in `forgit clean` correctly uses `git ls-files` with configurable args and handles filenames with backslashes.",
    "Installation succeeds via oh-my-zsh, Fisher, and manual sourcing methods.",
    "User can browse commit history with `glo` and view full diffs in fzf preview pane.",
    "User can interactively select files to add via `ga` and see them staged in Git.",
    "User can switch branches using `gsw` without typing full branch names."
  ]
